MESSAGE FROM OUR CEO & FOUNDER

My name is Alejandro Grande and I am CEO & Founder of Obinex, a web3 startup with the aim of developing a CEX (Centralized Exchange) with which to offer financial services at the launch of the MVP to evolve its structure into a service platform in its second development phase. We have in mind various products and services that can differentiate us from the competition, even since the launch of MVP. In addition to this, we will be the first UAE-based CEX to be launched via a Security Token.

On the other hand, and at the same time that we develop the CEX platform, we will begin the discovery phase of our own blockchain. This blockchain will differ from the rest in being the second centralized blockchain in the world (the first is BSN, owned by the Chinese government), but it will be the first in the world to have a layer 4 (the most innovative so far are layer 3). The goal of building a centralized blockchain is to put a stop once and for all to the lack of security caused by so many scams. The fact that it is centralized will be due to the fact that we will include a tool from the first day of launch that allows us to know the identity of all the transactions executed in the same network, thus being able to identify any person (or group of people) who commits any criminal act within said network.

As you may have imagined by reading these lines, this is a more than ambitious project, and that is why I am writing these lines to you. We are in one of the most difficult moments for any project, and it is the search for financing. Added to this, we must reckon with the uncertainty and fear generated by the fall of FTX, which became the second largest centralized exchange in the world, but at the same time presents us with a huge opportunity to show that things can be done. things differently from the start, and this is where you would come in.

We would like to give you an initial presentation of the project so that you could give us your opinion on how to improve the weak points that we may have and that we may not be realizing. We would also like you to invest in us (not in our project), thus becoming a Lead Investor, and of course, our best Advisor (as an advisor I think you would add great value to the team and the project).

Please, before rejecting the offer (if you were going to do so), give us 30 minutes of your time, since we consider that we have designed, with possible errors to correct, a competitive project and that, if we do things right from the start, Initially, it will offer many different opportunities for scaling at the technology and market level.

It works like this: you have a signals group, and as soon as one of your signals arrives in the group, your client will use the bot to make the trade, instead of doing it through the broker. The client benefits from the speed, as it's more dynamic to do it through the bot. The website has all the fields that the client just needs to fill in, such as: currency, take profit target, stop loss, value per trade, etc.

JÃºnior Silva, [12/1/2025 3:51 PM]
The difference is that, in addition to copying you faster and easier, the client will be able to use it to perform other operations of their choice. The software is free; just open a new tab, add a new currency pair, and enter. I can record an example video for you to see how it works in practice. How? Just send me a trade signal now, and I'll record my phone or computer screen and execute the operation you sent me through the bot. You'll see it's very simple, and the client doesn't need to provide personal data for this. It's very secure.

JÃºnior Silva, [12/1/2025 3:51 PM]
Give a trading signal, but it has to be a currency available for future trading on the BitGet exchange, as the bot currently only works there. We will make it available on other exchanges in the future.
